  "body": "<p>Last month we wrapped up a big packet project. </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605241725404-8TGLQE6UT13GQXMGUZO5/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>And now we can share what was in those little glassine envelopes galore. I snapped some photos of the process for the delightful little fabric flowers we made, also known as \"yo-yo's\". </p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"20b-dsc_1898.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605241755600-MKF8X3F1S9I1VFXCX7AJ/20b-dsc_1898.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"20c-dsc_1899.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605241755601-U8D9QEZGBJT2TC4M6YT8/20c-dsc_1899.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20d-dsc_1912.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605241756658-J98R5J0VFX9K80F2WBE2/20d-dsc_1912.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20e-dsc_0661.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605241757439-59C4EJJ9JMAB3I3KMCJN/20e-dsc_0661.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20f-dsc_0649.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605241793624-HKIFJIXBUKBM52YG1R6M/20f-dsc_0649.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20g-dsc_0650.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605241793710-IGMSHOXUFV3OSAPKD3H3/20g-dsc_0650.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>As you can see, we had to make a lot of these hand-sewn flowers. They can be found in <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/kits/story-hour?aff=6cc2c70f\">Studio Calico's March kit, Story Hour</a>. At the pre-sale for subscribers (I have been subbing for over a year), a portion of these kits were already sold out. In case you're thinking of getting one, here's the story: buy it now, before it's too late. And plant these little flowers on your paper projects.  </p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"20h-scmarchkit2.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605241835271-VMYO6BLET8DO4NKRXIXU/20h-scmarchkit2.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"20i-scmarch2012main283of329.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1605241836226-D3AQANBXK3E2VRAMFVYD/20i-scmarch2012main283of329.jpg\"/>"
}